{"tid":2488834,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"日本動畫業內人士評選改變歷史的動畫","createTime":"2021-04-14T13:23:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T19:40:22.000Z","uid":25345,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"e7835e91262797cd941326764c3c1b378525017b","tid":2488834,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T13:23:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://translate.google.com/website?sl=zh-CN&amp;tl=zh-TW&amp;prev=search&amp;u=http://n.sinaimg.cn/sinakd2021414s/190/w640h350/20210414/1237-knqqqmv6023278.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftranslate.google.com%2Fwebsite%3Fsl%3Dzh-CN%26tl%3Dzh-TW%26prev%3Dsearch%26u%3Dhttp%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Fsinakd2021414s%2F190%2Fw640h350%2F20210414%2F1237-knqqqmv6023278.jpg&h=9afe77fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n  朝日電視台在4月13日晚播出了由業內人士評選的改變日本動畫歷史的14部很厲害的動畫。這次的14部動畫是由76名製作過人氣動畫的職業製作人選出的。根據結果，被選出的是《煙囪城的普佩爾》、《BEASTARS》、《進擊的巨人》、《Great Pretender》、《EVA》、《少女與戰車》、《起風了》、《哆啦A夢》、《你的名字》、《紫羅蘭永恆花園》、《光之美少女》、《咒術回戰》、《高達》和《超時空要塞》這14部作品。"},{"pid":"014732de2f87127610722d1de0028e2a6df29385","tid":2488834,"uid":6142,"like":0,"dislike":33,"score":-33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T13:25:32.000Z","msg":"高達呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abcbce2bca2a6d3a3b3de3d96b8f9ef975a3e415","tid":2488834,"uid":299548,"like":9,"dislike":16,"score":-7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T13:26:45.000Z","msg":"刀劍呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmbz83nUK3vZdTh8jiB4NYLeUYD6dwSTqRd3WLPGWHS3L1?filename=ybiEdD3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FybiEdD3.png&h=4061de7d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5d21c587ac9c4e7b28db612befd22f5e005192be","tid":2488834,"uid":261873,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T13:29: